metadata.name: Infinite Room 01
metadata.description:
The infinite Room 01 stages the WORKCORE SOFA in an infinite one-minute loop.

This NFT is part of the INFINITE ROOMS, 3 pieces NFTs of digital furniture.

In case of possession of the 3 assets of this series, you unlock the sale of a unique and secret NFT which features 3 Infinite Rooms in a special format.
